data.description: Welcome to 15114  Foley Hill, a lovely 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in The Preserve at Medina. With brand new carpeting and fresh interior paint, this home offers a light and inviting atmosphere from the moment you step inside. As you enter the main floor, you'll be greeted by a spacious family room that seamlessly connects to the dining room. The kitchen, overlooking the dining area, features energy-efficient appliances and boasts beautiful granite countertops where you can easily add barstools for extra seating. Upstairs, you'll find all the bedrooms and a conveniently located laundry room. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering a generously sized walk-in closet. All occupants of the neighborhood have access to a large park and playground, perfect for outdoor activities and spending quality time with others. Located just outside of San Antonio, this home offers a fantastic location with easy access to 35 and 410. You'll also be close to the serene Medina River Natural Area, offering opportunities for outdoor adventures.     * Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D Tour.
